                  <ab type="history">Dabr. &#xD;
                     Currently there are three churches at the site: a small church of St. <persName ref="PRS6819Mary" type="tabot">Mary</persName> on the peak of the rock (visible from <placeName ref="INS0185SGM">Sǝddayto</placeName>), an older and a recent churches below in the compound. Pre-historic rock paintings have been discovered in the vicinity of the site. &#xD;</ab>
                  <ab type="tabot">
